rComments: One of the best professors that i have had in my university experience. She is very fair, understands the material and loves what she teaches. I would highly recommend you take this course if you are interested in learning Arabic or have a prior background in Arabic. It is truly an amazing course, which I loved to go to and learn a lot about Arabic
Great prof. The material is challenging and you have to consistently keep yourself up to date with the course but she is always there when you need her so you should be fine.
GREATLY APPRECIATE ALL THE HELP SHE GIVES HER STUDENTS AND THE LEVELS OF ENTHUSIASM IN HER TEACHING IS VERY NICE TO SEE.  DOESNT SPEAK ENGLISH TOO WELL BUT IS UNDERSTANDABLE.

The teacher is very helpful and very professional. She helps students A LOT and always taking in consideration their opinion in class. The class is very interesting and keeps you interested throughout the whole year. You have to study and attend class to get a good mark. I am very glad I took this class and I recommend every student to try it!
This course is very hard! Arabic is very hard! If you take this course I suggest you study what you learnt after each lecture.
